<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 20:09:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>民意调查：尽管失去了议会多数席位，内塔尼亚胡仍以微弱优势领先甘茨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/poll-netanyahu-holds-slim-lead-over-gantz-despite-losing-knesset-majority/00000191-d842-db7f-abd3-fbe79f950000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的联盟仅获得议会120个席位中的49个席位，而反对派将赢得71个席位。排除阿拉伯政党，反对党将获得61个席位</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 19:48:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/poll-netanyahu-holds-slim-lead-over-gantz-despite-losing-knesset-majority/00000191-d842-db7f-abd3-fbe79f950000</guid></item><item><title>“双方都厌倦了战争”：以色列前总理奥尔默特与巴勒斯坦前部长提出两国建议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/both-sides-are-tired-of-war-ex-pm-olmert-makes-two-state-proposal-with-ex-pa-minister/00000191-d7ae-d233-a5d3-ffbf31530000</link><description>该提案旨在结束加沙战争，建立临时阿拉伯安全存在，并为以 1967 年边界为基础、通过一条连接加沙和约旦河西岸的走廊建立独立的巴勒斯坦国铺平道路</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 17:52:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/both-sides-are-tired-of-war-ex-pm-olmert-makes-two-state-proposal-with-ex-pa-minister/00000191-d7ae-d233-a5d3-ffbf31530000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的“军事压力”谎言正在杀害人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-09/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-military-pressure-lies-are-killing-the-hostages/00000191-d740-dd5a-adf1-ff6f624d0000</link><description>根据内塔尼亚胡政府的命令，做出了明确的行动决定，继续搜寻加沙的隧道，以寻求“全面胜利”，尽管他们完全知道这将导致人质丧生</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 17:44:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-09/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-military-pressure-lies-are-killing-the-hostages/00000191-d740-dd5a-adf1-ff6f624d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促卡塔尔和埃及迫使哈马斯放弃新的加沙停火要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-urges-qatar-egypt-to-press-hamas-to-back-down-from-new-gaza-cease-fire-demands/00000191-d7ba-db7f-abd3-f7bf2c8b0000</link><description>拜登将于周一会见他的国家安全团队，以解决以色列与哈马斯的停火僵局。美国认为哈马斯的新要求过高，并认为在六名人质被谋杀后他们不应该得到奖励</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 17:17:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-urges-qatar-egypt-to-press-hamas-to-back-down-from-new-gaza-cease-fire-demands/00000191-d7ba-db7f-abd3-f7bf2c8b0000</guid></item><item><title>“疯狂的发明”：《犹太纪事报》关于哈马斯计划的报道受到密切关注</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/a-wild-invention-jewish-chronicles-report-on-hamas-plans-comes-under-scrutiny/00000191-d71b-dba7-a1ff-dfdf2c930000</link><description>上周，英国新闻网站报道称，哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔计划逃离加沙，并将以色列人质偷运到伊朗。这篇文章广为流传，但现在其准确性、来源和记者的资质都受到质疑</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 16:33:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/a-wild-invention-jewish-chronicles-report-on-hamas-plans-comes-under-scrutiny/00000191-d71b-dba7-a1ff-dfdf2c930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 339 天：以色列国防军呼吁加沙西北部居民撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-339-idf-calls-on-residents-of-northwest-gaza-to-evacuate/00000191-d792-db7f-abd3-f7b71b160000</link><description>哈马斯官员：如果以色列不接受拜登的停火提议，被扣押在加沙的以色列人质“将不会重见天日” ■ 以色列国防军呼吁加沙西北部居民在火箭弹从该地区向以色列发射后撤离 ■ 约旦谴责周日艾伦比与以色列边境发生枪击事件 ■ 从黎巴嫩发射的空中目标击中以色列北部的住宅楼 ■ 战争已过去 339 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 16:24:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-339-idf-calls-on-residents-of-northwest-gaza-to-evacuate/00000191-d792-db7f-abd3-f7b71b160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军警告真主党如果加沙谈判破裂，准备与以色列长期战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-warns-hezbollah-bracing-for-prolonged-fighting-with-israel-if-gaza-talks-collapse/00000191-d668-d457-a3f9-dfff8e830000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡内阁的一位消息人士告诉《国土报》，“即使是现在，战争已经过去近一年了，内塔尼亚胡所宣称的目标都没有实现”；尽管总理最近声称，让北方居民返回家园并不是正式的战争目标</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 16:08:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-warns-hezbollah-bracing-for-prolonged-fighting-with-israel-if-gaza-talks-collapse/00000191-d668-d457-a3f9-dfff8e830000</guid></item><item><title>以色列女子在特拉维夫海滩向部长本格维尔投掷沙子 警方起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/police-indicts-israeli-woman-for-throwing-sand-at-minister-ben-gvir-at-tel-aviv-beach/00000191-d72b-db7f-abd3-f7afd4080000</link><description>27 岁的诺亚·戈登伯格 (Noa Goldenberg) 因袭击公务员和妨碍警察而被起诉，每项指控将面临最高三年的监禁。她因涉嫌向国家安全部长扔湿泥而被捕</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 15:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/police-indicts-israeli-woman-for-throwing-sand-at-minister-ben-gvir-at-tel-aviv-beach/00000191-d72b-db7f-abd3-f7afd4080000</guid></item><item><title>吞并、驱逐和以色列定居点：内塔尼亚胡为加沙战争的下一阶段做好准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/annexation-expulsion-and-settlements-netanyahu-gears-up-for-next-phase-of-gaza-war/00000191-d739-dba7-a1ff-dfff26830000</link><description>战争进入新阶段并不是从多师机动或对敌人腹地的大胆袭击开始的。相反，它是通过一份官僚声明而来的，并将让本杰明·内塔尼亚胡梦想着他的支持者将视之为一生的成就</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 15:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/annexation-expulsion-and-settlements-netanyahu-gears-up-for-next-phase-of-gaza-war/00000191-d739-dba7-a1ff-dfff26830000</guid></item><item><title>是什么让以色列学生为伊朗情报部门工作？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/what-made-an-israeli-student-work-for-iranian-intelligence/00000191-d656-deec-add7-de57ca1e0000</link><description>伊朗特工正在通过社交媒体接触以色列人，试图招募他们。辛贝特担心越来越多的以色列人愿意与他们合作</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 15:17:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/what-made-an-israeli-student-work-for-iranian-intelligence/00000191-d656-deec-add7-de57ca1e0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么特朗普和万斯不会谴责塔克·卡尔森和他否认大屠杀的朋友</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-trump-and-vance-wont-condemn-tucker-carlson-and-his-holocaust-denying-pals/00000191-d69a-db58-afbb-defefa580000</link><description>至少唐纳德·特朗普是一贯的。多年来他一直在为反犹太主义者和大屠杀否认者辩护。但作为共和党总统候选人，他与塔克·卡尔森的接近对美国、以色列和全球犹太人构成了明显而现实的危险</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-trump-and-vance-wont-condemn-tucker-carlson-and-his-holocaust-denying-pals/00000191-d69a-db58-afbb-defefa580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-约旦边境的致命袭击可能使阿卜杜拉国王陷入政治雷区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/the-attack-at-the-jordan-border-crossing-poses-a-grave-political-threat-to-king-abdullah/00000191-d5e6-deaf-a1f1-ddf71e6f0000</link><description>约旦国王巧妙地平衡了内部对以色列的愤怒和维持外交关系的努力。就在约旦人即将投票选出新议会的几天前，袭击者与一个关键支持部落的联系使他的事情变得复杂</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:44:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/the-attack-at-the-jordan-border-crossing-poses-a-grave-political-threat-to-king-abdullah/00000191-d5e6-deaf-a1f1-ddf71e6f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列因发布威胁人质母亲的视频而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arrested-for-publishing-threatening-video-against-hostages-mother/00000191-d63c-dec1-add7-f7ff4c890000</link><description>警方逮捕了一名来自以色列北部的男子，据称他发布了一段视频，威胁要袭击已在加沙被关押超过 11 个月的 Matan 的母亲 Einav Zangauker</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:24:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arrested-for-publishing-threatening-video-against-hostages-mother/00000191-d63c-dec1-add7-f7ff4c890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队告诉家人，在被谋杀的加沙人质上发现了防御伤痕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/defense-wounds-found-on-murdered-gaza-hostages-israeli-army-tells-families/00000191-d5a6-df60-a79b-d5fffe670000</link><description>以色列国防军上周取回了人质的尸体，并表示他们在士兵抵达前不久被处决。据一名人质亲属称，家人被告知隧道内场面混乱，人质身上发现有防御伤痕</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:31:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/defense-wounds-found-on-murdered-gaza-hostages-israeli-army-tells-families/00000191-d5a6-df60-a79b-d5fffe670000</guid></item><item><title>枪、辫子和警惕的眼睛：这位埃塞俄比亚以色列艺术家拒绝陈词滥调</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/guns-braids-and-watchful-eyes-this-ethiopian-israeli-artist-refuses-to-be-a-cliche/00000191-d239-d214-a393-d7b917740000</link><description>雷切尔·安约 (Rachel Anyo) 掌控了自己的叙事，创作出具有挑衅性的作品，直面黑人女性气质、潜在的暴力和社会期望，并大胆拒绝强加给她的谦虚</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:30:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/guns-braids-and-watchful-eyes-this-ethiopian-israeli-artist-refuses-to-be-a-cliche/00000191-d239-d214-a393-d7b917740000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡请求法院阻止在即将上映的电影中播放他的审讯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-court-to-block-airing-of-his-interrogation-in-upcoming-film/00000191-d5e9-deaf-a1f1-ddff45940000</link><description>耶路撒冷法院在提交请愿书后不久就驳回了请愿书，距离“比比档案”计划在多伦多电影节首映几个小时</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-court-to-block-airing-of-his-interrogation-in-upcoming-film/00000191-d5e9-deaf-a1f1-ddff45940000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列袭击了叙利亚境内与伊朗有关的地点，包括化学武器设施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/report-israel-strikes-iranian-sites-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d537-d25e-a1f7-d7bf512e0000</link><description>叙利亚官方媒体称以色列连夜对哈马附近发动袭击 反对派战争监察员称七人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 07:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/report-israel-strikes-iranian-sites-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d537-d25e-a1f7-d7bf512e0000</guid></item><item><title>所有以色列人都会为司法部长对司法系统的痴迷付出代价，甚至可能是内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/all-israelis-will-pay-for-levins-obsession-with-the-judiciary-maybe-even-netanyahu/00000191-d347-d25e-a1f7-d7cf2b6f0000</link><description>以色列最高法院的法官们别无选择，被迫拒绝命令司法部长遵守法律条文，召开一年多没有开会的司法任命委员会，以便它可以根据资历制度选举新的最高法院院长</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 04:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/all-israelis-will-pay-for-levins-obsession-with-the-judiciary-maybe-even-netanyahu/00000191-d347-d25e-a1f7-d7cf2b6f0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙医务人员：周一有 20 名巴勒斯坦人死亡；黎巴嫩无人机炸伤两名以色列士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article-live/reports-israel-struck-several-targets-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d4b2-d83f-a3d9-ddfbf7310005</link><description>辛贝特逮捕了三名计划发动袭击的巴勒斯坦人 ■ 以色列国防军表示，由于有可疑人员存在的情报，士兵们推迟了联合国车队 ■ 美国国务院表示，预计对美籍土耳其公民的死亡进行“彻底”、“透明”的调查 ■ 拜登预计将召开国家安全会议小组讨论停火/人质释放协议谈判状况</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 03:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article-live/reports-israel-struck-several-targets-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d4b2-d83f-a3d9-ddfbf7310005</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长预计推迟任命新最高法院院长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-expected-to-delay-appointment-of-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d331-dd1c-a19b-d33157550000</link><description>一位与司法部长亚里夫·莱文关系密切的人士表示，“他不会做一个好孩子，安静地接受裁决”，他指的是最高法院要求他必须任命一位新总统的裁决，“但他也不会违反这一裁决”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 20:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-expected-to-delay-appointment-of-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d331-dd1c-a19b-d33157550000</guid></item></channel></rss>